name: my body my religion #1
description:
Religion in general means a system, tradition, something that binds or something that is not chaotic and in Javanese philosophy, ageman is clothing.
in my personal understanding religion is the body, where this body binds my soul or the clothes of the soul and the body has a very regular system and every human being has the same system and body even though the shape and color may be different but have the same system and function.
